Record Class TuiParser.ParsedArgs

java.lang.Object
java.lang.Record
it.polimi.ingsw.cg04.client.view.tui.TuiParser.ParsedArgs
Record Components:
coordGroups - groups of coordinate lists provided with -c flags
intList - additional integer arguments
boxMapList - list of box-type-to-value maps parsed from -k and -m flags
singleInt - a single integer parsed (e.g., game or tile index)
string - a string argument (e.g., color or nickname)
coord1 - first coordinate parsed (if applicable)
coord2 - second coordinate parsed (if applicable)
accept - whether the user accepted an option (e.g., boolean flag)
planetIdx - selected planet index (if applicable)
Enclosing class:
TuiParser

Represents the result of parsing command arguments.
